r-bottom-style: none !important; background-color: transparent !important; =
display: inline-block;">
<span>[9]</span>
</a></p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Meanwhile here=E2=80=99s <a href=3D"https://li=
nk.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/29049995.262538/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21=
iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDktMTQvaGVkZ2UtZnVuZHMtYXJlLWJldHRpbm=
